dc_description_s: This polygon shapefile represents the political boundaries for the 113th United States Senate. The official membership is current as of August 18, 2014. This layer is part of the 2014 ESRI Data and Maps collection for ArcGIS 10.2.U.S. 113th Senate provides the locations of U.S. states and the senators that represent them, primarily for national planning applications.
